> 2004/10/27 (Haypo)
   - Translate physical object class in english (big part, was very boring and long)
   - Fix physical engine : characters move 1 pixel to the bottom of the map (collision test was uncorrected), and support closed maps : characters can walk on map bottom border (code was broken)
   - Sky also use tile
   - Use map preview instead loading all datas
   - It's now possible to change data & locale directories in config file
